###MITWSH: 1 kuttaro -> 2 kuttara.
###PERILIPTIKA DES KAI VIVLIO GIA LEPTOMERIES

-Profash:
	1. Inidia xrwmatinhs -> Xrwmoswmata
	2. Kentroswmatia stous polous
	3. Sxhmatismos Atraktou & Apodiorganwsh pyrhnikhs membranhs kai pyrhniskoy

-Metafash:
	1. Metakinhsh xrwmoswmatwn sto ishmerino(kentro) epipedo tou kyttarou
	2. Megisth syspeirwsh [Symphknwsh(fainontai sto mikroskopoio)]
		###PROSOXH: TO ENA DIPLA STO ALLO 

-Anafash:
	1. To Kentromeridio diaireite kai oi mikroswlhniskoi traboun ka8e aderlfh
	xrwmatida pros ton ka8e polo

-Telofash: 
	1. Oi xrwmatides ftanoun stous polous
	2. Xrwmoswmata -> Inidia Xrwmatinhs
	3. Apodiorganwsh atraktou & epanemfanish pyrhnikwn membranwn kai pyrhniskou



###PIO LEPTOMERES EJHGHSH

Mitwsh -> (i) Pyrhnikh Diairesh, (ii) Kyttaroplasmatikh Diairesh

(i) Pyrhnikh Diairesh -> Profash, Metafash, Anafash, Telofash

	###Profash:
		Einai to megalytero meros se diarkeia ths mitwshs. Ta inidia xrwmatinhs
		arxizoun na perielissontai & na symphknwnontai wste na dhmiourghsoun
		thn xarakthristikh morfh twn xrwmoswmatwn. Auth h morfh apoteleitai apo
		*2 adelfes xrwmatides* pou enwnontai me to *kentromeridio*. Oi adelfes
		xrwmatides einai apotelesma autodiplasiasmou genetikou ylikou pou egine
		sth mesofash. O logos pou to genetiko yliko menei mesa se xrwmoswmata einai
		aplos. Den prepei na spasei oute na xa8ei tipota kata th metafora tou 
		genetikou ylikou sta 8ygatrika kyttara. Meta sxhmatizetai h atraktos.
		Sta zwika kyttara arxika diplasiazontai ta kentroswmatia ta opoia
		metakinountai pros tous dyo polous. Auta provaloun tous mikroswlhniskous
		pou einai aktinwta nhmata kai siga siga apo tous mikroswlhniskous 
		sxhmatizetai h atraktos. Sta fytika kyttara den sxhmatizetai atraktos
		ka8ws den yparxoun kentroswmatia. Molis sxhmatistei h atraktos 
		apodiorganwnetai h pyrhnikh membranh kai o pyrhniskos wste na eisvaloun
		oi mikroswlhniskoi mesa sto xwro pou katalambane o pyrhnas kai na enw8oun
		ta kentromeridia twn xrwmoswmatwn.

	###Metafash:
		Me thn enarjh ths metafashs ta xrwmoswmata egkataleipoun tis tyxaies 8eseis
		pou eixan kata th profash kai arxizoun na metakinountai kata mhkos twn 
		nhmatwn ths atraktou, pros to ishmerino epipedo tou kyttarou. Molis ftasoun
		exoun topo8eth8ei parallhla pros auto(to ena dipla sto allo ) oi adelfes
		xrwmatides ka8e xrwmoswmatos. Epishs sth metafash synexizetai h symphknwsh
		twn inidiwn xrwmatinhs. Katalhgei ews to megisto ba8mo symphknwshs giauto
		kai einai diakrita sto mikroskopio apo oso sta ypoloipa stadia tou 
		kyttarikou kyklou.

	##Anafash:
		Sthn anafash diaireite to kentromeridio ka8e xrwmoswmatos. Ka8e adelfh
		xrwmatida anejarthtopoieitai apo thn allh. Auto ginetai ka8ws oi 
		mikroswlhniskoi traboun anti8eta ka8emia me apotelesma na dhmiourgh8ei
		anti8eth eljh sto kentromeridio kai oi dyo adelfes xrwmatides apospountai
		pros tous dyo anti8etous polous h ka8emia.  

	##Telofash:
		Molis ftasei h ka8e adelfh xrwmatida ston polo jekinaei h telofash. Einai
		akribws h anti8eth diadikasia ths profashs. Apodiorganwnetai h atraktos
		kai janaemfanizetai oi pyrhnikoi fakeloi (mebranes). Se ka8ena apo autous
		ta xrwmoswmata janaginontai inidia xrwmatinhs kai epanasxhmatizetai o 
		pyrhniskos.

(ii) Kyttaroplasmatikh Diairesh -> Diaforetikh se zwika kai se fytika kyttara

#Se Zwika
	-Sto ypsos tou hsimerinou epipedou tou kyttarou sxhmatizetai enas periferiakos
	daktylios apo inidia aktinhs. Autos o daktylios me thn parodo tou xronou steneuei
	mexri telika na dixotomhsei to kyttaro.	

#Se Fytika
	-Molis h pyrhnikh diairesh ftasei sthn anafash, sthn perioxh tou ishmerinou 
	dhmiourgeitai apo mikroswlhniskous ena plegma pou onomazetai fragmoplasths.
	Apo to fragmoplasth prokyptoun ta kyttarika tyxwmata twn dyo 8ygatrikwn kyttarwn.
